sectionHeading: Regular traffic reports will resume Wednesday January 11 at 6:30 a.m.

incidentType: Traffic Alert for I-75S at 142 MM in Scott Co:
location: Roadway shutdown until at least 6 p.m. due to a large amount of wood debris from an earlier collision.

incidentType: Traffic Alert for I-75S at 142 MM in Scott Co:
location: Detour:  Exit 144 to Corinth, to US-25S, back to I-75S at Exit 136.

incidentType: Traffic Alert for I-75S at 142 MM in Scott Co:
location: Update 5:46 p.m. - One or two lanes possibly open soon.  Scene could be cleared in about 1 hour.
